Title: Usual Suspects
Writer: Kevin Hopps, Bob Kane (Batman creator), Mark D. Bright (character: Raquel Ervin/Rocket)
Actors: Lacey Chabert, Crispin Freeman, Miss Kittie, Stephanie Lemelin
Plot: The team gets a new member and a new mission - a mission that may finally expose all of the team's secrets ... and all of their lies!
